column2: SELECT   SpecObj.specObjID,    SpecObj.z as redshift,    SpecObj.ra,    SpecObj.dec,   galaxy.u,    galaxy.g,    galaxy.r,    galaxy.i,    galaxy .z,    zooSpec.spiral,   zooSpec.elliptical    FROM SpecObj, zooSpec, galaxy    WHERE zooSpec.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID   AND SpecObj.class=&&&   AND SpecObj.sourceType = &&&   AND (  zooSpec.p_el > #   OR zooSpec.p_cw > #   OR zooSpec.p_acw > #     OR zooSpec.p_mg > #)   AND zooSpec.uncertain = #    ORDER BY SpecObj.z DESC
